bg-cream group transition-colors\" href=\"/services/web-design\"><p class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[0.85rem] tracking-wide group-hover:text-orange transition-colors mb-0.5\">Web Design &amp; Hosting</p><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/55 text-[0.78rem] leading-[1.45]\">Local-SEO websites, custom builds, hosted by us.</p></a></li><li><a role=\"menuitem\" class=\"block px-4 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-cream group transition-colors\" href=\"/services/marketing\"><p class=\"font-eurostile uppercase text-navy text-[0.85rem] tracking-wide group-hover:text-orange transition-colors mb-0.5\">Online Marketing</p><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/55 text-[0.78rem] leading-[1.45]\">Local SEO, Google Ads, GBP management.</p></a></li></ul></div></div></li><li><a class=\"font-exo font-bold text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy/70 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/pricing\">Pricing</a></li><li><a class=\"font-exo font-bold text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy/70 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/scorecard\">Scorecard</a></li><li><a class=\"font-exo font-bold text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy/70 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/faq\">FAQ</a></li><li><a class=\"font-exo font-bold text-xs tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy/70 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></li></ul><a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-sm\" href=\"/contact\">Get Started <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a></div><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Open menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"mobile-menu\" class=\"md:hidden w-11 h-11 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-1.5 cursor-pointer\"><span class=\"block w-6 h-0.5 bg-navy transition-all \" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"block w-6 h-0.5 bg-navy transition-all \" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"block w-6 h-0.5 bg-navy transition-all \" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></button></nav><div id=\"mobile-menu\" class=\"md:hidden overflow-hidden transition-[max-height] duration-300 ease-out border-t border-navy/10 max-h-0\"><ul class=\"flex flex-col py-2 px-6 bg-cream\"><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/about\">About</a></li><li class=\"border-b border-navy/5\"><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"w-full py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer\"><span>Services</span><svg width=\"10\" height=\"10\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"transition-transform duration-200 \"><polyline points=\"6 9 12 15 18 9\"></polyline></svg></button><div class=\"overflow-hidden transition-[max-height] duration-300 ease-out max-h-0\"><ul class=\"pb-3 pl-3 border-l-2 border-orange/30 ml-1\"><li><a class=\"block py-2.5 px-3 font-exo font-semibold text-[0.8rem] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-navy/75 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/services/it-support\">IT Support &amp; Security</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-2.5 px-3 font-exo font-semibold text-[0.8rem] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-navy/75 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/services/web-design\">Web Design &amp; Hosting</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-2.5 px-3 font-exo font-semibold text-[0.8rem] tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-navy/75 hover:text-orange transition-colors\" href=\"/services/marketing\">Online Marketing</a></li></ul></div></li><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/pricing\">Pricing</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/scorecard\">Scorecard</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/faq\">FAQ</a></li><li><a class=\"block py-4 font-exo font-bold text-sm tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-orange transition-colors border-b border-navy/5\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></li><li class=\"py-4\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary w-full justify-center\" href=\"/contact\">Get Started <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a></li></ul></div></header><main class=\"font-rajdhani\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What does IT support for small businesses include?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"IT support for small businesses includes monitoring your systems for problems before they cause downtime, resolving technical issues when they come up, keeping your software and devices updated, and protecting your business from security threats. We handle email, hosting and website maintenance, cloud backups and more. At Tech 4 Underdogs, it also means you reach a real person who already knows your setup — not a call center reading from a script.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How much does IT support cost for a small business?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Tech 4 Underdogs offers three tiers of IT support priced per user, per month — starting at $56/user/mo for our On Watch package. All packages include monitoring and real human support. There's a 3-user minimum. Pricing scales based on response time, security depth, and the level of access you need. Schedule a conversation and we'll help you figure out what makes sense for your business.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Do I need managed IT support if I only have a few employees?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes — and in many ways, small businesses need it more. A business with two or five employees doesn't have an IT department to catch problems early. A single outage, a ransomware attack, or a week of slow systems can cost far more than a monthly support plan. Managed IT support gives you the same protection a larger company gets, sized and priced for your operation.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What cybersecurity protection do small businesses actually need?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"At minimum, small businesses need active threat monitoring, safe email practices, regular software patches and updates, and a basic security policy. Many small businesses are targeted specifically because they're perceived as easier to breach than larger companies. Our security protection is layered and sized for your budget — not an enterprise checklist you'll never actually use.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What happens when something breaks? How fast do you respond?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Response time depends on your support package. Our On Watch plan includes next-business-day response, On Guard responds within 4 business hours, and On Call delivers priority 1–2 hour response. In every case, you're reaching a real person who knows your business — not waiting on a ticket queue to be claimed by someone unfamiliar with your setup.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can I get IT support without a long-term contract?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes. Tech 4 Underdogs IT support plans are month-to-month. We use a simple service agreement, but there's no long-term lock-in. We want to earn your trust over time — not hold it hostage.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How much does a small business website cost?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Our Ready to Run local SEO websites start at $149 per month (under 15 pages) — with hosting, maintenance, security, and ongoing updates included. There's no large upfront bill. For businesses that need a fully custom or WordPress build, pricing is based on scope; those sites require no ongoing contract and are yours outright. Either way, one flat monthly cost covers everything.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What is local SEO and does my small business website need it?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Local SEO is the process of optimizing your website and online presence so your business shows up when someone nearby searches for what you offer — for example, 'plumber near me' or 'bakery in [your city].' If your business depends on local customers, local SEO is not optional. Without it, you're invisible to the people most likely to buy from you.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What's included in your website hosting and maintenance?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Every website we build includes managed hosting on infrastructure we control, SSL security, uptime monitoring, regular software updates and patches, and ongoing maintenance. If something needs attention, you reach the same team that built your site — not a stranger reading from a ticket. Content changes are handled on an ongoing basis based on your plan, including unlimited text and photo updates upon request.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How long does it take to build a small business website?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Our Ready to Run local SEO websites are designed for fast turnaround — typically within a few weeks depending on how quickly we can gather your content and approvals. Custom WordPress or full-stack builds take longer based on complexity. In every case, we don't disappear after launch — the same team that builds your site stays with it.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What's the difference between a basic website and a local SEO website?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"A basic website exists online. A local SEO website is built specifically to rank in search results when local customers look for what you do — it loads fast, uses location-targeted keywords, is structured to signal relevance to Google, and includes a properly configured Google Business Profile connection. Every site we build is SEO-ready from day one.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Do I own my website?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"For custom and WordPress builds — yes, the site is yours. For our Ready to Run monthly plans, the site lives on our managed infrastructure as part of the service agreement. If you cancel, we don't hold you hostage. We'll discuss transition options and offer a fair buyout should you want to gain control and move your site. We're always transparent about this upfront — no surprises.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How do I get my small business to show up on Google?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Two main ways: Local SEO (organic search) and Google Ads (paid search). Local SEO involves optimizing your website and Google Business Profile so Google understands where you are, who you serve, and what you offer. Google Ads puts your business in front of people actively searching right now, even before you've built organic rankings. For most small businesses, the right answer is both — starting with a strong local SEO foundation for organic growth.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What is Google My Business and why does it matter for local businesses?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Google Business Profile (formerly Google My Business) is the listing that appears when someone searches for your business or for businesses like yours near their location. It shows your hours, location, reviews, photos, and contact information. An incomplete or neglected profile costs you customers every day. Tech 4 Underdogs actively manages, updates and optimizes your profile — so it's always accurate, current, and working in your favor.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How much should a small business spend on Google Ads?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"There's no one-size-fits-all answer — it depends on your market, competition, and goals. What we do know is that Google Ads without proper management wastes money fast. Our Google Ads management service is $399/mo (plus ad spend, which goes directly to Google with no markup). We set it up, manage it actively, and give you a plain-language report every month so you can see exactly what's working.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What's the difference between Local SEO and Google Ads?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Local SEO builds your organic presence over time — it's not instant, but it compounds. Google Ads delivers immediate visibility for people searching right now, but stops the moment you stop paying. For small businesses, we recommend Local SEO as the foundation and Google Ads as the accelerator when you need faster results. Together, they cover both short-term and long-term local visibility.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How do I know if my online marketing is actually working?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"You should be seeing it in calls, form submissions, and foot traffic — not just dashboard metrics you don't understand. We provide clear monthly reporting in plain language. No mystery metrics. No agency-speak. We tell you what's working, what we're improving, and what we're seeing in your market — every single month.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How long before I see results from local SEO?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Honest answer: Local SEO is not an overnight solution. Most businesses begin seeing meaningful movement in 3–6 months, depending on your market, competition, and starting point. The businesses that see results fastest are the ones with consistent, quality work done every month — which is exactly how we operate. We stay close to your results and adjust based on what the data shows.\"}}]}</script><section class=\"bg-cream overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"section-container section-y\"><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr] gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center\"><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><p class=\"eyebrow mb-5\"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>Frequently Asked Questions</p><h1 class=\"h-section text-navy mb-6\"><span class=\"italic text-outlined-navy\">Real answers</span><span> to the questions </span><span>small business owners </span><span class=\"italic text-orange\">ask most.</span></h1><div class=\"lg:hidden flex justify-center mb-8\"><img alt=\"Archie answering questions\" width=\"620\" height=\"626\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full max-w-[280px] sm:max-w-[340px] h-auto object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-FAQ.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-FAQ.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-FAQ.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"/></div><p class=\"body-text max-w-[640px] text-[1.05rem]\">What IT support actually costs, how long SEO takes, whether you really own your website — answered clearly, without the runaround.</p></div><div class=\"hidden lg:flex justify-end\"><img alt=\"Archie answering questions\" width=\"620\" height=\"626\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full max-w-[460px] xl:max-w-[520px] h-auto object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-FAQ.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-FAQ.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FArchie-FAQ.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"/></div></div><div class=\"mt-10 lg:mt-12 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md border border-navy/10 p-4 lg:p-5\"><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-3 sm:gap-4\"><span class=\"font-exo font-extrabold text-xs lg:text-sm tracking-[0.22em] uppercase text-orange flex-shrink-0 sm:border-r sm:border-navy/10 sm:pr-5\">Jump to ↓</span><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2 flex-1\"><a href=\"#it-support-faq\" class=\"font-exo font-bold text-xs lg:text-[0.85rem] tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-navy text-center bg-cream/60 hover:bg-orange hover:text-white border border-navy/10 transition-colors rounded-lg px-4 py-3\">IT Support &amp; Security</a><a href=\"#web-design-faq\" class=\"font-exo font-bold text-xs lg:text-[0.85rem] tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-navy text-center bg-cream/60 hover:bg-orange hover:text-white border border-navy/10 transition-colors rounded-lg px-4 py-3\">Web Design &amp; Hosting</a><a href=\"#online-marketing-faq\" class=\"font-exo font-bold text-xs lg:text-[0.85rem] tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-navy text-center bg-cream/60 hover:bg-orange hover:text-white border border-navy/10 transition-colors rounded-lg px-4 py-3\">Online Marketing</a></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"it-support-faq\" class=\"scroll-mt-24 bg-white\"><div class=\"section-container section-y\"><div class=\"max-w-[860px] mx-auto\"><p class=\"eyebrow mb-5\"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>IT Support &amp; Security</p><h2 class=\"h-section text-navy mb-10\"><span>IT support questions, </span><span class=\"italic text-orange\">answered plainly.</span></h2><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border border-navy/10 shadow-sm overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"border-b border-navy/10 last:border-b-0\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"w-full flex items-start gap-4 text-left px-6 sm:px-8 py-5 cursor-pointer group\" aria-expanded=\"true\" aria-controls=\"it-support-faq-panel-0\"><span class=\"text-orange font-extrabold text-lg flex-shrink-0 w-5 text-center leading-none mt-0.5 transition-transform duration-200\" style=\"transform:rotate(45deg)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">+</span><span class=\"font-eurostile text-navy text-[0.9rem] sm:text-[1rem] tracking-wide uppercase flex-1 leading-[1.35]\">What does IT support for small businesses include?</span></button><div id=\"it-support-faq-panel-0\" class=\"grid transition-all duration-300 ease-out\" style=\"grid-template-rows:1fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/75 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.75] pl-[3.25rem] sm:pl-[3.75rem] pr-6 sm:pr-8 pb-6\">IT support for small businesses includes monitoring your systems for problems before they cause downtime, resolving technical issues when they come up, keeping your software and devices updated, and protecting your business from security threats. We handle email, hosting and website maintenance, cloud backups and more. At Tech 4 Underdogs, it also means you reach a real person who already knows your setup — not a call center reading from a script.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"border-b border-navy/10 last:border-b-0\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"w-full flex items-start gap-4 text-left px-6 sm:px-8 py-5 cursor-pointer group\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"it-support-faq-panel-1\"><span class=\"text-orange font-extrabold text-lg flex-shrink-0 w-5 text-center leading-none mt-0.5 transition-transform duration-200\" style=\"transform:rotate(0deg)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">+</span><span class=\"font-eurostile text-navy text-[0.9rem] sm:text-[1rem] tracking-wide uppercase flex-1 leading-[1.35]\">How much does IT support cost for a small business?</span></button><div id=\"it-support-faq-panel-1\" class=\"grid transition-all duration-300 ease-out\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/75 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.75] pl-[3.25rem] sm:pl-[3.75rem] pr-6 sm:pr-8 pb-6\">Tech 4 Underdogs offers three tiers of IT support priced per user, per month — starting at $56/user/mo for our On Watch package. All packages include monitoring and real human support. There&#x27;s a 3-user minimum. Pricing scales based on response time, security depth, and the level of access you need. Schedule a conversation and we&#x27;ll help you figure out what makes sense for your business.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"border-b border-navy/10 last:border-b-0\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"w-full flex items-start gap-4 text-left px-6 sm:px-8 py-5 cursor-pointer group\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"it-support-faq-panel-2\"><span class=\"text-orange font-extrabold text-lg flex-shrink-0 w-5 text-center leading-none mt-0.5 transition-transform duration-200\" style=\"transform:rotate(0deg)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">+</span><span class=\"font-eurostile text-navy text-[0.9rem] sm:text-[1rem] tracking-wide uppercase flex-1 leading-[1.35]\">Do I need managed IT support if I only have a few employees?</span></button><div id=\"it-support-faq-panel-2\" class=\"grid transition-all duration-300 ease-out\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/75 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.75] pl-[3.25rem] sm:pl-[3.75rem] pr-6 sm:pr-8 pb-6\">Yes — and in many ways, small businesses need it more. A business with two or five employees doesn&#x27;t have an IT department to catch problems early. A single outage, a ransomware attack, or a week of slow systems can cost far more than a monthly support plan. Managed IT support gives you the same protection a larger company gets, sized and priced for your operation.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"border-b border-navy/10 last:border-b-0\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"w-full flex items-start gap-4 text-left px-6 sm:px-8 py-5 cursor-pointer group\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"it-support-faq-panel-3\"><span class=\"text-orange font-extrabold text-lg flex-shrink-0 w-5 text-center leading-none mt-0.5 transition-transform duration-200\" style=\"transform:rotate(0deg)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">+</span><span class=\"font-eurostile text-navy text-[0.9rem] sm:text-[1rem] tracking-wide uppercase flex-1 leading-[1.35]\">What cybersecurity protection do small businesses actually need?</span></button><div id=\"it-support-faq-panel-3\" class=\"grid transition-all duration-300 ease-out\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/75 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.75] pl-[3.25rem] sm:pl-[3.75rem] pr-6 sm:pr-8 pb-6\">At minimum, small businesses need active threat monitoring, safe email practices, regular software patches and updates, and a basic security policy. Many small businesses are targeted specifically because they&#x27;re perceived as easier to breach than larger companies. Our security protection is layered and sized for your budget — not an enterprise checklist you&#x27;ll never actually use.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"border-b border-navy/10 last:border-b-0\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"w-full flex items-start gap-4 text-left px-6 sm:px-8 py-5 cursor-pointer group\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"it-support-faq-panel-4\"><span class=\"text-orange font-extrabold text-lg flex-shrink-0 w-5 text-center leading-none mt-0.5 transition-transform duration-200\" style=\"transform:rotate(0deg)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">+</span><span class=\"font-eurostile text-navy text-[0.9rem] sm:text-[1rem] tracking-wide uppercase flex-1 leading-[1.35]\">What happens when something breaks? How fast do you respond?</span></button><div id=\"it-support-faq-panel-4\" class=\"grid transition-all duration-300 ease-out\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/75 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.75] pl-[3.25rem] sm:pl-[3.75rem] pr-6 sm:pr-8 pb-6\">Response time depends on your support package. Our On Watch plan includes next-business-day response, On Guard responds within 4 business hours, and On Call delivers priority 1–2 hour response. In every case, you&#x27;re reaching a real person who knows your business — not waiting on a ticket queue to be claimed by someone unfamiliar with your setup.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"border-b border-navy/10 last:border-b-0\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"w-full flex items-start gap-4 text-left px-6 sm:px-8 py-5 cursor-pointer group\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"it-support-faq-panel-5\"><span class=\"text-orange font-extrabold text-lg flex-shrink-0 w-5 text-center leading-none mt-0.5 transition-transform duration-200\" style=\"transform:rotate(0deg)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">+</span><span class=\"font-eurostile text-navy text-[0.9rem] sm:text-[1rem] tracking-wide uppercase flex-1 leading-[1.35]\">Can I get IT support without a long-term contract?</span></button><div id=\"it-support-faq-panel-5\" class=\"grid transition-all duration-300 ease-out\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/75 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.75] pl-[3.25rem] sm:pl-[3.75rem] pr-6 sm:pr-8 pb-6\">Yes. Tech 4 Underdogs IT support plans are month-to-month. We use a simple service agreement, but there&#x27;s no long-term lock-in. We want to earn your trust over time — not hold it hostage.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-10 text-center\"><p class=\"font-exo font-semibold text-navy/60 text-sm tracking-wide mb-4\">Have a question that&#x27;s not here?</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary justify-center\" href=\"/contact\">Talk to a Real Person<!-- --> <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a></div><p class=\"font-exo font-semibold text-navy/45 text-[0.7rem] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mt-5\">We respond within one business day. No sales pressure, ever.</p></div></div></div></section><section id=\"web-design-faq\" class=\"scroll-mt-24 bg-cream\"><div class=\"section-container section-y\"><div class=\"max-w-[860px] mx-auto\"><p class=\"eyebrow mb-5\"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>Web Design &amp; Hosting</p><h2 class=\"h-section text-navy mb-10\"><span>Website questions, </span><span class=\"italic text-outlined-navy\">no runaround.</span></h2><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border border-navy/10 shadow-sm overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"border-b border-navy/10 last:border-b-0\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"w-full flex items-start gap-4 text-left px-6 sm:px-8 py-5 cursor-pointer group\" aria-expanded=\"true\" aria-controls=\"web-design-faq-panel-0\"><span class=\"text-orange font-extrabold text-lg flex-shrink-0 w-5 text-center leading-none mt-0.5 transition-transform duration-200\" style=\"transform:rotate(45deg)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">+</span><span class=\"font-eurostile text-navy text-[0.9rem] sm:text-[1rem] tracking-wide uppercase flex-1 leading-[1.35]\">How much does a small business website cost?</span></button><div id=\"web-design-faq-panel-0\" class=\"grid transition-all duration-300 ease-out\" style=\"grid-template-rows:1fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/75 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.75] pl-[3.25rem] sm:pl-[3.75rem] pr-6 sm:pr-8 pb-6\">Our Ready to Run local SEO websites start at $149 per month (under 15 pages) — with hosting, maintenance, security, and ongoing updates included. There&#x27;s no large upfront bill. For businesses that need a fully custom or WordPress build, pricing is based on scope; those sites require no ongoing contract and are yours outright. Either way, one flat monthly cost covers everything.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"border-b border-navy/10 last:border-b-0\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"w-full flex items-start gap-4 text-left px-6 sm:px-8 py-5 cursor-pointer group\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"web-design-faq-panel-1\"><span class=\"text-orange font-extrabold text-lg flex-shrink-0 w-5 text-center leading-none mt-0.5 transition-transform duration-200\" style=\"transform:rotate(0deg)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">+</span><span class=\"font-eurostile text-navy text-[0.9rem] sm:text-[1rem] tracking-wide uppercase flex-1 leading-[1.35]\">What is local SEO and does my small business website need it?</span></button><div id=\"web-design-faq-panel-1\" class=\"grid transition-all duration-300 ease-out\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/75 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.75] pl-[3.25rem] sm:pl-[3.75rem] pr-6 sm:pr-8 pb-6\">Local SEO is the process of optimizing your website and online presence so your business shows up when someone nearby searches for what you offer — for example, &#x27;plumber near me&#x27; or &#x27;bakery in [your city].&#x27; If your business depends on local customers, local SEO is not optional. Without it, you&#x27;re invisible to the people most likely to buy from you.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"border-b border-navy/10 last:border-b-0\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"w-full flex items-start gap-4 text-left px-6 sm:px-8 py-5 cursor-pointer group\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"web-design-faq-panel-2\"><span class=\"text-orange font-extrabold text-lg flex-shrink-0 w-5 text-center leading-none mt-0.5 transition-transform duration-200\" style=\"transform:rotate(0deg)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">+</span><span class=\"font-eurostile text-navy text-[0.9rem] sm:text-[1rem] tracking-wide uppercase flex-1 leading-[1.35]\">What&#x27;s included in your website hosting and maintenance?</span></button><div id=\"web-design-faq-panel-2\" class=\"grid transition-all duration-300 ease-out\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/75 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.75] pl-[3.25rem] sm:pl-[3.75rem] pr-6 sm:pr-8 pb-6\">Every website we build includes managed hosting on infrastructure we control, SSL security, uptime monitoring, regular software updates and patches, and ongoing maintenance. If something needs attention, you reach the same team that built your site — not a stranger reading from a ticket. Content changes are handled on an ongoing basis based on your plan, including unlimited text and photo updates upon request.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"border-b border-navy/10 last:border-b-0\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"w-full flex items-start gap-4 text-left px-6 sm:px-8 py-5 cursor-pointer group\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"web-design-faq-panel-3\"><span class=\"text-orange font-extrabold text-lg flex-shrink-0 w-5 text-center leading-none mt-0.5 transition-transform duration-200\" style=\"transform:rotate(0deg)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">+</span><span class=\"font-eurostile text-navy text-[0.9rem] sm:text-[1rem] tracking-wide uppercase flex-1 leading-[1.35]\">How long does it take to build a small business website?</span></button><div id=\"web-design-faq-panel-3\" class=\"grid transition-all duration-300 ease-out\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/75 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.75] pl-[3.25rem] sm:pl-[3.75rem] pr-6 sm:pr-8 pb-6\">Our Ready to Run local SEO websites are designed for fast turnaround — typically within a few weeks depending on how quickly we can gather your content and approvals. Custom WordPress or full-stack builds take longer based on complexity. In every case, we don&#x27;t disappear after launch — the same team that builds your site stays with it.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"border-b border-navy/10 last:border-b-0\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"w-full flex items-start gap-4 text-left px-6 sm:px-8 py-5 cursor-pointer group\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"web-design-faq-panel-4\"><span class=\"text-orange font-extrabold text-lg flex-shrink-0 w-5 text-center leading-none mt-0.5 transition-transform duration-200\" style=\"transform:rotate(0deg)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">+</span><span class=\"font-eurostile text-navy text-[0.9rem] sm:text-[1rem] tracking-wide uppercase flex-1 leading-[1.35]\">What&#x27;s the difference between a basic website and a local SEO website?</span></button><div id=\"web-design-faq-panel-4\" class=\"grid transition-all duration-300 ease-out\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/75 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.75] pl-[3.25rem] sm:pl-[3.75rem] pr-6 sm:pr-8 pb-6\">A basic website exists online. A local SEO website is built specifically to rank in search results when local customers look for what you do — it loads fast, uses location-targeted keywords, is structured to signal relevance to Google, and includes a properly configured Google Business Profile connection. Every site we build is SEO-ready from day one.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"border-b border-navy/10 last:border-b-0\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"w-full flex items-start gap-4 text-left px-6 sm:px-8 py-5 cursor-pointer group\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"web-design-faq-panel-5\"><span class=\"text-orange font-extrabold text-lg flex-shrink-0 w-5 text-center leading-none mt-0.5 transition-transform duration-200\" style=\"transform:rotate(0deg)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">+</span><span class=\"font-eurostile text-navy text-[0.9rem] sm:text-[1rem] tracking-wide uppercase flex-1 leading-[1.35]\">Do I own my website?</span></button><div id=\"web-design-faq-panel-5\" class=\"grid transition-all duration-300 ease-out\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/75 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.75] pl-[3.25rem] sm:pl-[3.75rem] pr-6 sm:pr-8 pb-6\">For custom and WordPress builds — yes, the site is yours. For our Ready to Run monthly plans, the site lives on our managed infrastructure as part of the service agreement. If you cancel, we don&#x27;t hold you hostage. We&#x27;ll discuss transition options and offer a fair buyout should you want to gain control and move your site. We&#x27;re always transparent about this upfront — no surprises.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-10 text-center\"><p class=\"font-exo font-semibold text-navy/60 text-sm tracking-wide mb-4\">Ready to talk about your website?</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary justify-center\" href=\"/contact\">Get a Free Consultation<!-- --> <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a><a class=\"btn btn-secondary justify-center\" href=\"/#services\">See Pricing<!-- --> <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a></div><p class=\"font-exo font-semibold text-navy/45 text-[0.7rem] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mt-5\">We respond within one business day. No sales pressure, ever.</p></div></div></div></section><section id=\"online-marketing-faq\" class=\"scroll-mt-24 bg-white\"><div class=\"section-container section-y\"><div class=\"max-w-[860px] mx-auto\"><p class=\"eyebrow mb-5\"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>Online Marketing</p><h2 class=\"h-section text-navy mb-10\"><span>Marketing questions from owners </span><span class=\"italic text-orange\">who&#x27;ve been burned before.</span></h2><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl border border-navy/10 shadow-sm overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"border-b border-navy/10 last:border-b-0\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"w-full flex items-start gap-4 text-left px-6 sm:px-8 py-5 cursor-pointer group\" aria-expanded=\"true\" aria-controls=\"online-marketing-faq-panel-0\"><span class=\"text-orange font-extrabold text-lg flex-shrink-0 w-5 text-center leading-none mt-0.5 transition-transform duration-200\" style=\"transform:rotate(45deg)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">+</span><span class=\"font-eurostile text-navy text-[0.9rem] sm:text-[1rem] tracking-wide uppercase flex-1 leading-[1.35]\">How do I get my small business to show up on Google?</span></button><div id=\"online-marketing-faq-panel-0\" class=\"grid transition-all duration-300 ease-out\" style=\"grid-template-rows:1fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/75 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.75] pl-[3.25rem] sm:pl-[3.75rem] pr-6 sm:pr-8 pb-6\">Two main ways: Local SEO (organic search) and Google Ads (paid search). Local SEO involves optimizing your website and Google Business Profile so Google understands where you are, who you serve, and what you offer. Google Ads puts your business in front of people actively searching right now, even before you&#x27;ve built organic rankings. For most small businesses, the right answer is both — starting with a strong local SEO foundation for organic growth.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"border-b border-navy/10 last:border-b-0\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"w-full flex items-start gap-4 text-left px-6 sm:px-8 py-5 cursor-pointer group\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"online-marketing-faq-panel-1\"><span class=\"text-orange font-extrabold text-lg flex-shrink-0 w-5 text-center leading-none mt-0.5 transition-transform duration-200\" style=\"transform:rotate(0deg)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">+</span><span class=\"font-eurostile text-navy text-[0.9rem] sm:text-[1rem] tracking-wide uppercase flex-1 leading-[1.35]\">What is Google My Business and why does it matter for local businesses?</span></button><div id=\"online-marketing-faq-panel-1\" class=\"grid transition-all duration-300 ease-out\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/75 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.75] pl-[3.25rem] sm:pl-[3.75rem] pr-6 sm:pr-8 pb-6\">Google Business Profile (formerly Google My Business) is the listing that appears when someone searches for your business or for businesses like yours near their location. It shows your hours, location, reviews, photos, and contact information. An incomplete or neglected profile costs you customers every day. Tech 4 Underdogs actively manages, updates and optimizes your profile — so it&#x27;s always accurate, current, and working in your favor.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"border-b border-navy/10 last:border-b-0\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"w-full flex items-start gap-4 text-left px-6 sm:px-8 py-5 cursor-pointer group\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"online-marketing-faq-panel-2\"><span class=\"text-orange font-extrabold text-lg flex-shrink-0 w-5 text-center leading-none mt-0.5 transition-transform duration-200\" style=\"transform:rotate(0deg)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">+</span><span class=\"font-eurostile text-navy text-[0.9rem] sm:text-[1rem] tracking-wide uppercase flex-1 leading-[1.35]\">How much should a small business spend on Google Ads?</span></button><div id=\"online-marketing-faq-panel-2\" class=\"grid transition-all duration-300 ease-out\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/75 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.75] pl-[3.25rem] sm:pl-[3.75rem] pr-6 sm:pr-8 pb-6\">There&#x27;s no one-size-fits-all answer — it depends on your market, competition, and goals. What we do know is that Google Ads without proper management wastes money fast. Our Google Ads management service is $399/mo (plus ad spend, which goes directly to Google with no markup). We set it up, manage it actively, and give you a plain-language report every month so you can see exactly what&#x27;s working.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"border-b border-navy/10 last:border-b-0\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"w-full flex items-start gap-4 text-left px-6 sm:px-8 py-5 cursor-pointer group\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"online-marketing-faq-panel-3\"><span class=\"text-orange font-extrabold text-lg flex-shrink-0 w-5 text-center leading-none mt-0.5 transition-transform duration-200\" style=\"transform:rotate(0deg)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">+</span><span class=\"font-eurostile text-navy text-[0.9rem] sm:text-[1rem] tracking-wide uppercase flex-1 leading-[1.35]\">What&#x27;s the difference between Local SEO and Google Ads?</span></button><div id=\"online-marketing-faq-panel-3\" class=\"grid transition-all duration-300 ease-out\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/75 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.75] pl-[3.25rem] sm:pl-[3.75rem] pr-6 sm:pr-8 pb-6\">Local SEO builds your organic presence over time — it&#x27;s not instant, but it compounds. Google Ads delivers immediate visibility for people searching right now, but stops the moment you stop paying. For small businesses, we recommend Local SEO as the foundation and Google Ads as the accelerator when you need faster results. Together, they cover both short-term and long-term local visibility.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"border-b border-navy/10 last:border-b-0\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"w-full flex items-start gap-4 text-left px-6 sm:px-8 py-5 cursor-pointer group\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"online-marketing-faq-panel-4\"><span class=\"text-orange font-extrabold text-lg flex-shrink-0 w-5 text-center leading-none mt-0.5 transition-transform duration-200\" style=\"transform:rotate(0deg)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">+</span><span class=\"font-eurostile text-navy text-[0.9rem] sm:text-[1rem] tracking-wide uppercase flex-1 leading-[1.35]\">How do I know if my online marketing is actually working?</span></button><div id=\"online-marketing-faq-panel-4\" class=\"grid transition-all duration-300 ease-out\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/75 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.75] pl-[3.25rem] sm:pl-[3.75rem] pr-6 sm:pr-8 pb-6\">You should be seeing it in calls, form submissions, and foot traffic — not just dashboard metrics you don&#x27;t understand. We provide clear monthly reporting in plain language. No mystery metrics. No agency-speak. We tell you what&#x27;s working, what we&#x27;re improving, and what we&#x27;re seeing in your market — every single month.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"border-b border-navy/10 last:border-b-0\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"w-full flex items-start gap-4 text-left px-6 sm:px-8 py-5 cursor-pointer group\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"online-marketing-faq-panel-5\"><span class=\"text-orange font-extrabold text-lg flex-shrink-0 w-5 text-center leading-none mt-0.5 transition-transform duration-200\" style=\"transform:rotate(0deg)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">+</span><span class=\"font-eurostile text-navy text-[0.9rem] sm:text-[1rem] tracking-wide uppercase flex-1 leading-[1.35]\">How long before I see results from local SEO?</span></button><div id=\"online-marketing-faq-panel-5\" class=\"grid transition-all duration-300 ease-out\" style=\"grid-template-rows:0fr\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden\"><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/75 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.75] pl-[3.25rem] sm:pl-[3.75rem] pr-6 sm:pr-8 pb-6\">Honest answer: Local SEO is not an overnight solution. Most businesses begin seeing meaningful movement in 3–6 months, depending on your market, competition, and starting point. The businesses that see results fastest are the ones with consistent, quality work done every month — which is exactly how we operate. We stay close to your results and adjust based on what the data shows.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-10 text-center\"><p class=\"font-exo font-semibold text-navy/60 text-sm tracking-wide mb-4\">Want to see what straightforward marketing looks like?</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary justify-center\" href=\"/contact\">Talk to a Real Person<!-- --> <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a><a class=\"btn btn-secondary justify-center\" href=\"/#services\">See Pricing<!-- --> <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a></div><p class=\"font-exo font-semibold text-navy/45 text-[0.7rem] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mt-5\">We respond within one business day. No sales pressure, ever.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-teal-gradient overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"section-container section-y\"><div class=\"max-w-[820px] mx-auto text-center\"><p class=\"eyebrow eyebrow-dark mb-5 justify-center inline-flex\"><span class=\"eyebrow-mark\">✺</span>Ready when you are</p><h2 class=\"h-section mb-6\"><span class=\"text-white\">Still have questions? </span><span class=\"italic text-orange\">That&#x27;s what the first conversation is for.</span></h2><p class=\"body-text body-text-dark max-w-[620px] mx-auto mb-9\">We don&#x27;t start with a pitch. We start by understanding your business, what&#x27;s working, and what isn&#x27;t — a straightforward conversation with someone who already knows the terrain.</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary btn-lg justify-center\" href=\"/contact\">Talk to a Real Person <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a><a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-lg justify-center\" href=\"/#services\">See How We Help <span aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</span></a></div><p class=\"font-exo font-semibold text-white/50 text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mt-6\">We respond within one business day. No sales pressure, ever.</p></div></div></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-white border-t border-navy/10\"><div class=\"section-container pt-16 pb-10\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-[1.4fr_1fr_1fr_1.2fr] gap-10 lg:gap-12 items-start\"><div><img alt=\"Tech 4 Underdogs\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"180\" height=\"58\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"h-auto w-40 mb-4\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FTech-4-Underdogs-logo.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FTech-4-Underdogs-logo.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2FTech-4-Underdogs-logo.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75\"/><p class=\"font-exo font-medium text-navy/70 text-[0.9rem] leading-[1.7] max-w-[320px] mb-6\">Reliable, affordable IT, websites, and online marketing — built for the small businesses doing serious work.</p><div class=\"flex gap-2\"></div></div><di